&lt;p&gt;Litify is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;QA Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Product &amp;amp; Engineering team! This is a high-impact, AI-first role where you will own quality end-to-end within an agile squad. In this role, you will play a crucial part in ensuring the quality of our legal software, which is built on the Salesforce platform. The ideal candidate has a strong background in both manual and automated testing and will thrive in a hands-on, team-oriented, and fast-paced agile environment. We are actively transforming how QA works at Litify; shifting from traditional manual test execution to an AI-augmented model where AI agents perform initial test passes and human QA engineers focus on reviewing AI-generated results, exploratory edge-case testing, and making critical judgment calls on quality and risk.&lt;/p&gt;
